| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0780 — Recovery Inhibition (threeam)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1921fd57-67d0-54bc-8d6b-5430fd0e27a4"
